264
00:09:43,718 --> 00:09:46,416
What? Uh, no, no, no.
No, it's not.

265
00:09:46,460 --> 00:09:48,462
This is my house,
my production.

266
00:09:48,505 --> 00:09:49,463
The show goes on.

