and I heard the camera
adds like 10 pounds.

309
00:11:10,805 --> 00:11:12,328
Is that true?

310
00:11:12,372 --> 00:11:13,982
So when was the last time
you saw Morris?

311
00:11:14,026 --> 00:11:15,810
Honestly, I ain't seen him
all day.

312
00:11:15,854 --> 00:11:17,116
I was dealing with work stuff

313
