right up
until we started filming.

314
00:11:18,944 --> 00:11:20,946
And where were you
when Morris's body was found?

315
00:11:20,989 --> 00:11:22,904
In my office.

316
00:11:22,948 --> 00:11:24,079
And how would
you characterize

317
00:11:24,123 --> 00:11:26,342
Aaron's relationship
with Morris?

318
00:11:29,345 --> 00:11:30,956
It's important
you tell the truth.

319
00:11:33,175 --> 00:11:35,525
They didn't always agree about
the direction of the show.

320
00:11:35,569 --> 00:11:37,310
But my son,
he would never hurt anyone.

321
00:11:44,665 --> 00:11:47,450
Hey, do we really have
to do this in here?

322
00:11:47,494 --> 00:11:48,713
Yes, we do, son.

323
