you will lose your job.

337
00:12:22,834 --> 00:12:23,965
Of course I'll cooperate.

338
00:12:26,272 --> 00:12:27,229
Good man.

339
00:12:29,492 --> 00:12:30,711
Alright.

340
00:12:30,755 --> 00:12:31,799
I'll leave you to it.

341
00:12:35,716 --> 00:12:36,848
I didn't kill Morris.

342
00:12:41,113 --> 00:12:44,986
When I saw him lying there,
like Patrick...

343
00:12:45,030 --> 00:12:46,379
I understand.

344
00:12:46,422 --> 00:12:48,120
But it was common knowledge
that you and Morris

345
00:12:48,163 --> 00:12:49,730
weren't on
the best of terms.

346
00:12:49,774 --> 00:12:53,125
Who are you with? TMZ?

347
00:12:53,168 --> 00:12:54,735
You still feeding off my grief, you vultures?!
Come on, guys.

348
00:12:54,779 --> 00:12:55,736
Morris,
what are you doing, man?
Get 'em out of here, man!

349
00:12:55,780 --> 00:12:57,738
Get out of here now!
Go!

350
00:12:57,782 --> 00:12:59,827
Yeah, what he did
