with Flow, and, um...

472
00:17:30,577 --> 00:17:33,014
Yeah, he said
that he'd rather walk

473
00:17:33,058 --> 00:17:35,277
than to deal
with Flow's nonsense.

474
00:17:35,321 --> 00:17:36,539
Um...

475
00:17:36,583 --> 00:17:38,541
It was a good thing, too.

476
00:17:38,585 --> 00:17:40,804
A devastating loss
for the music industry today,

477
00:17:40,848 --> 00:17:44,808
as Calvin Yard, one half
of the popular duo Flex n' Flow,

478
00:17:44,852 --> 00:17:47,159
