485
00:18:04,915 --> 00:18:07,440
Um, Flow was shot
seven times.

486
00:18:08,919 --> 00:18:11,183
Yeah.

487
00:18:11,226 --> 00:18:13,402
That was my first homicide.

488
00:18:13,446 --> 00:18:14,925
I'll never forget it.

489
00:18:14,969 --> 00:18:16,840
It changes you.

490
00:18:16,884 --> 00:18:21,149
I did not have anything to do
with Calvin's death.

491
00:18:21,193 --> 00:18:22,629
But at the time of
his murder, all the talk was --

492
00:18:22,672 --> 00:18:23,934
That was garbage, man.

493
00:18:23,978 --> 00:18:25,153
All garbage.

494
00:18:25,197 --> 00:18:26,328
I loved Calvin
like a brother.

495
00:18:26,372 --> 00:18:28,330
You know, this --

496
00:18:28,374 --> 00:18:29,897
this is
straight-up exploitive.

497
00:18:29,940 --> 00:18:32,856
Calvin's murder was solved
decades ago, and you know it.

498
00:18:32,900 --> 00:18:36,295
A man named Gary Brown
was convicted of Flow's murder.

499
00:18:36,338 --> 00:18:38,775
It turns out Flow
was sleeping with Gary's wife.

500
00:18:38,819 --> 00:18:42,257
